init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm still the second best," he said to himself.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Larry beamed as John's expression turned to one of jealousy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John looked at the mug in his hand and grinned.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The same cardboard legend was still on it.
